Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.04,0:00:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Here? I get to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight Sparkle said you were\Ncoming to Canterlot for a visit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...and asked if\NI might accommodate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much, princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.38,0:00:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.69,0:00:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, really. This is so nice of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.36,0:00:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but it isn't nothing.\NIt's everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I just don't know what to say\Nbut thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you... Thank you...\NThank you, thank you, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,-You are very welc...\N-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your luggage, mademoiselle?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave you to get settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.50,0:00:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where would you like me to put these?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.35,0:01:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Opal, do you know what\NI love about Canterlot?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.02,0:01:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have been born in Ponyville,\Nbut I am a Canterlot pony at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I know that we are here\Nto pick up some fabrics for the shop...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.60,0:02:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...but Twilight was such a dear\Nto get me that suite at the castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...I simply must make her something\Nto express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.14,0:02:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,An outfit for her birthday party\Nthis weekend! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.32,0:02:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you just love it\Nhere, Opalescence?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.73,0:02:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse our interruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jet Set and this\Nis my wife, Upper Crust.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw you from across the café\Nand just have to find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get that\Nsimply marvelous chapeau?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, this old thing?\NOh, it's just something I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.06,0:02:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! Hayseed Turnip Truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.63,0:02:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We met at the big hoedown\Nin Ponyville last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... Yes... Of course. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Real good!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from... Ponyville?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.06,0:02:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, ye... yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She sure is! She's a real big time\Nfancy pants dressmaker there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably made that real purty\Nthing she's got on her head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.68,0:03:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it looked a little... country.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.38,0:03:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it wasn't something you\Ncould get here in Canterlot, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they seemed real nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Looked a little country."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"Not something you could\Nget in Canterlot."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you something\Nworthy of Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get started right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This new design is very ambitious...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I've already written\Nto Twilight to let her know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...she'll have something beyond\Nfabulous to wear to her party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.22,0:03:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancypants?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.59,0:04:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, that's one way\Nto make the introduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.82,0:04:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry. I didn't see you there.\NI've just got so many bags...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I was trying to get back\Nto my suite at the castle and...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:12.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're staying at the castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.03,0:04:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... The princess invited me\Nto stay in one of the suites.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... A pony with\Nexpensive taste, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.98,0:04:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... It's for an ensemble\NI'm making for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Her birthday is in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, I am really sorry\NI bumped into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.42,0:04:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You are obviously somepony\Nworth bumping into.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.36,0:04:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, listen. I have a VIP box reserved\Nat the Wonderbolts Derby this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you... Would you be so kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...as to join me and a few\Nof my companions there, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm... uh... I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd love to see you there, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Pro: seeing the derby from a VIP box\Nis a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Con: going to the derby cuts\Ninto the amount of time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.53,0:05:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...I have to finish Twilight's outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.25,0:05:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Pro: Fancypants is *the* most\Nimportant pony in Canterlot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,His stamp of approval could\Nmean big things for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.77,0:05:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Con: Twilight's party might not be\Nas sophisticated as a derby...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...but that doesn't mean\NI shouldn't put all of my energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...into creating her birthday ensemble.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.90,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My Ponyville friends will appreciate\Nmy hard work more than anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to let them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.15,0:05:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Opal, I am going to the Wonderbolts\NDerby as a guest of Fancypants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me.. Excuse me... Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:06:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity! Jolly good to see you!\NSo glad you could make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.79,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Everypony, this is Rarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She is staying at Canterlot Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.42,0:06:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Fillies and gentlecolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Wonderbolts Derby!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.47,0:06:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The competitors are taking their\Nplaces at the starting line...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the race will begin momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be rooting for Rapidfire, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.69,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sure to take home the grand prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he has\Na chance against Fleetfoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's Fleetfoot by a nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.49,0:06:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo, Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.15,0:06:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, how did you know\NFleetfoot would be victorious?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My friend Rainbow Dash\Ntalks about her all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She says what Fleetfoot lacks\Nin size, she makes up for in speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And who is this Rainbow Dash?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.68,0:07:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the... the Wonderbolts'\Ntrainer, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying at Canterlot Castle AND she knows\Nthe pegasus training the Wonderbolts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you all this was\Nan important pony.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.13,0:07:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Three cheers for Rarity,\Nmy new favorite party guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.99,0:07:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hip hip, hurray! Hip hip, hurray!\NHip hip, hurray!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.53,0:07:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...and then I said: "Please,\Nthat isn't a hat, darling."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"That's a natural disaster, that\Nsomehow landed atop your head!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are a delight, Rarity.\NAn absolute delight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You simply must attend my\Nart gallery opening this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.16,0:08:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. I'd love to, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And let's not forget my charity\Nauction tomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds wonderful, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course there's a seat for you\Nat my dinner party tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm flattered. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just I have a project I really\Nneed to get started on and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.40,0:08:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.40,0:08:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I may as well close down the whole\Ngallery if you can't attend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.72,0:08:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,My auction is for charity,\Ndear. For charity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And my dinner party will be\Na disaster if you don't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wonderful!\N-Disaster averted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we'll be spending a few\Nmore days here, Opalescence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out bumping into\NFancypants like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.34,0:08:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...was the best thing that's\Never happened to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course finishing\NTwilight's dress in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...for her birthday party\Nis still my top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.15,0:08:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't possibly disappoint\Nthe Canterlot elite...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...by rejecting their\Ninvitations, now can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be the toast of the town,\Nthe girl on the go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the type of pony\Neverypony, everypony should know{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll be the one to watch,\Nthe girl in the flow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.84,0:09:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the type of pony\Neverypony, everypony should know{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Becoming as popular\Nas popular can be{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.09,0:09:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Making my mark, making my mark\Nin high society{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.15,0:09:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the belle of the ball,\Nthe star of the show, yeah{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the type of pony\Neverypony, everypony should know{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.02,0:09:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}See how they hang on\Nevery word that I speak{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.04,0:09:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My approving glance\Nis what they all seek{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the crème de la crème,\Nnot just another Jane Doe{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:10:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the type of pony\Neverypony should know{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At home, at the opera,\Non a fancy yacht{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Becoming the talk,\Nthe talk of all of Canterlot{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.12,0:10:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm the crème de la crème,\Nnot just another Jane Doe, yeah{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.88,0:10:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the type of pony\Neverypony, everypony should know{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because I'm the type of pony{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, I'm the type of pony{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, I'm the type of pony\Neverypony should know{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I hope I haven't forgotten anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Me... too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.73,0:10:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We better get going.\NI must get back to Ponyville...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.24,0:10:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...with enough time\Nto finish Twilight's ensemble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.31,0:11:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.54,0:11:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dearest Rarity, your\Npresence is requested..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,"...at the Canterlot Garden\NParty tomorrow afternoon."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.57,0:11:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Yours, Jet Set and Upper Crust."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The Canterlot Garden Party!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, next to the Galloping Gala that is\N*the* premier event of Canterlot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh. But if I go,\NI'll miss Twilight's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I don't go, my new\Nreputation in Canterlot...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...as a Very Important\NPony might be ruined!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I might never be invited to another\Nhigh society event again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.14,0:11:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend's birthday – Very Important Pony...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.43,0:11:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just too important.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"My dear Twilight. I am afraid..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.34,0:11:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"...I won't be able to make it\Nto your birthday party tomorrow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"...because..."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because poor Opal is quite ill!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And she is in no condition to make\Nthe long journey back to Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:12:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"I do hope you understand.\NYour friend, Rarity."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose this means you don't\Nneed me to bring down your bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I will need some\Nhelp unpacking them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.35,0:12:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. Too little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.96,0:12:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Garden party, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.97,0:12:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,SURPRISE!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And SWOOSH! And right before\Nshe hit the ground, SHOOM, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.65,0:12:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.88,0:12:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you...\NHow did you... Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.65,0:12:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to her. She's so excited\Nto see us, she can hardly talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.29,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What I mean to say is,\Nwhat are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When I got your letter saying\Nyou were stuck in Canterlot...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.21,0:12:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...I asked Pinkie Pie if it\Nwouldn't be too much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.69,0:12:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...to move my birthday party here,\Nso you wouldn't have to miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Balloons are super easy to pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. First you get me a suite\Nat Canterlot Castle and now this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what to say, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you start by saying what\Nyou're doing in that fancy getup.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This? Uh.. Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.34,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I always put on something a little fancy\Nwhen Opal's feeling under the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers her right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, poor Opal.\NWhere is the sick darling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.39,0:13:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh... she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I am so sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.01,0:13:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's resting on the bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.93,0:13:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor baby. She looks awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that my dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so simple. So practical.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So... ME!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.65,0:13:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the perfect dress\Nfor my birthday party!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know how glad\NI am to hear you say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.85,0:14:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When I told the princess that I was\Nmoving the party to Canterlot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...she was kind enough to offer us\Nthe Canterlot Castle ballroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.87,0:14:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it fancy pants?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancypants!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I... mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...where did you find the time\Nto put up all these decorations?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.84,0:14:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I never leave home\Nwithout my party cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.92,0:14:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought about having\Nmy birthday outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...but they're having another party\Non the castle grounds today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.54,0:14:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,LET'S PARTY!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No reason I can't at least\Nmake an appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, I'm so glad you made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity! So happy to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.36,0:15:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have missed\Nthis for the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.20,0:15:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, what is that\Nscent you're wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.97,0:15:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells like...\NIs that cake frosting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I always dab a little frosting\Nbehind my ears before I go out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.93,0:15:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, who doesn't like\Nthe smell of cake frosting?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.77,0:16:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.43,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, all this talk about cake\Nhas made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Think I'll go and see what's\Non the hors d'oeuvre table.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-I must say, you do look like a...\N-Oh, yes, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I left the bath water\Nrunning in my suite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I really should go check on Opal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.30,0:16:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that Princess Celestia?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to use the little filly's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.46,0:17:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I get anypony more punch?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have to go to do the...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...thing with the... stuff, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.91,0:17:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... What's with the croquet mallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-[What croquet mallet?]\N-Duh! The one in your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.22,0:17:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that croquet mallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.36,0:17:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I... well, I... you know,\Nthe truth is... the truth is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you at that other\Nparty in the garden?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, I'm surprised at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, let me explain! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.57,0:17:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't realized you were\Nsuch a savvy businesspony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You must understand! I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.59,0:17:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All of those ponies look so posh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And with the Grand\NGalloping Gala coming up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...I bet you could totally get\Nsome of them to buy your dresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Very smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.72,0:17:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh... wwwhyyy, yes! Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want you to think\NI was being rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.87,0:17:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...so that's exactly\Nthe reason I didn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The one and only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. You didn't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:18:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You should totally go\Nover there and mingle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you really are the best\Nfriend a pony could ever ask for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.70,0:18:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why I ever thought\Nyou wouldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,See you girls later!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.39,0:18:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.86,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're your friends. I'm sure they won't\Nmind if we check out the party too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you guys! Let's show 'em\Nhow to party Ponyville style!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How come y'all aren't\Ndoin' any gardenin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.29,0:18:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a garden party, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you believe what\Nthat pony is wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just so plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.04,0:19:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Might I ask where\Nyou got you ensemble?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, yes. Yes, you may.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A very, very close friend of mine\Nfrom Ponyville made it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.13,0:19:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponyville? You don't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I do say. Her name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fancypants! Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.05,0:19:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to show you...\Nthis thing that's over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.90,0:19:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,On the other side of the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In a moment, my dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This lovely filly from Ponyville\Nwas just about to tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...who made her charming dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That dress? Oh, come now.\NWho cares? It's just a plain old...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.67,0:19:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't be so modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.27,0:19:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This dress you made is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We all think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You know these ponies?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.88,0:20:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes, I do know them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.03,0:20:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They may not be as sophisticated\Nas some of you Canterlot ponies...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...but they are my best friends\Nand they are without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.89,0:20:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...the most important ponies I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.65,0:20:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Important ponies"? These ruffians?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I, for one, find them charmingly rustic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.80,0:20:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I think the dress you made\Nfor your friend is lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.01,0:20:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare say every mare\Nin Canterlot will be wanting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'd like to place my order right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you should get two, hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.24,0:20:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes. Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you introduce me\Nto your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.43,0:20:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,With pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.71,0:21:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dear Princess Celestia."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"I wanted to tell you about the important\Nlesson I learned during my visit."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I would like to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned that no matter\Nwhere you go in life...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.18,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...you should never forget that you are\Nthe product of your home and your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is something always\Nto be proud of, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A very valuable lesson to have learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It certainly is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,...but might I ask that\Nwe hurry things up a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.83,0:21:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oooh nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.91,0:21:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Synced by Nathan2000\Nhttp://mlp.wikia.com/wiki/User:Nathan2000
